----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This program is a simple vocabulary trainer based on text files.
For the syntax of the vocabulary db, see the example file (voc_ex.txt).

There is no installation required, simply run the script SVocTrainer.pl in a shell.

Requirements:
- a perl distribution comparable with Perl >= 5.8

For more information and the latest version, see our project site at svoctrainer.sourceforge.net
There is also a documentation file, see "DOC".
